%F A097314 a(n) = S(n, 38) + S(n-1, 38) = S(2*n, 2*sqrt(10)), with Chebyshev polynomials of the second kind. See A049310 for the triangle of S(n, x) = U(n, x/2) coefficients. S(-1, x) := 0 =: U(-1, x).
